title: No Quarantine for Mexican President After Meeting Coronavirus-Infected Governor, Official Says
description: Mexican health officials revealed that President Andres Manuel Lopez Obrador (AMLO) will not go into quarantine after meeting with a governor who later tested positive for the novel coronavirus. He reportedly will not seek other protective measures as well, o…
